snippet.title: New Mexico EAS Amber Alert 09/08/2019
snippet.description:
A CAP alert. Alert heard here was decoded by one of the sources I monitor. You can see the expanded text on the DASDEC's screen.

UPDATE: Three days after this alert was originally broadcast, the girl was found dead.
